flowchart LR
  subgraph Sources
    S1[Image repositories]
    S2[Metadata / annotations]
    S3[External web candidates]
  end

  S1 ---|ingest| I[Ingestion service]
  S2 ---|ingest| I
  S3 ---|crawl| I

  I --> P[Preprocessing]
  P --> Aug[Augmentation]
  Aug --> Store[Feature store / Blob storage]
  Store --> Split[Dataset split: train / val / OE / OOD]

  Split --> Prep[Dataset materialization & caching]
  Prep --> Training[Training pipeline: TrainingWorkflow.run()]
  Training --> Checkpoint[Checkpoint & logs]
  Checkpoint --> AdapterExport[Export adapter bundle (SD-LoRA)]
  AdapterExport --> Registry[Adapter Registry (/models/adapters)]

  Registry --> Router[Router calibration & runtime]
  Router --> Inference[Inference pipeline (vlm_pipeline)]
  Inference --> Client[Client / Notebook / Service]

  %% Monitoring
  Checkpoint --> Metrics[BER / OOD metrics / Eval]
  Metrics -->|If fail| Training
  Metrics -->|If pass| Deploy[Serve / Deploy adapters]

  classDef io fill:#f3f4f6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
  class Store,Registry,Checkpoint io;